snippet.title: Paladins - Become a Champion
snippet.description:
Follow us for updates!
http://facebook.com/paladinsgame
http://twitter.com/paladinsgame

Introducing the newest game from Hi-Rez Studios - Paladins: Champions of the Ream!  Paladins offers deep strategy and in-match character progression through decks of collectible cards, which enhance a character’s core set of abilities. The game will be free-to-play for PC and current-generation consoles, and will enter Early Access later this year. Players can sign up now at www.paladinsgame.com.
